22:58.566 --> 23:03.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Here to talk about how
Ivanka Trump's clothing
is made is Matea Gold
of The Washington Post.

23:06.033 --> 23:08.800 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She's part of a team of
reporters that investigated
the Ivanka Trump brand's
manufacturing practices.

23:09.666 --> 23:11.766 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Matea, thanks for joining us.

23:11.766 --> 23:16.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
In your story, you said that
the Ivanka Trump fashion line
had retail sales of about $100

23:17.433 --> 23:19.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
million last year.

23:19.500 --> 23:21.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
What does she make, and
where does she make them?

23:21.566 --> 23:25.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MATEA GOLD, The Washington
Post: The Ivanka Trump brand,
which the first daughter still

23:25.333 --> 23:30.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
