26:59.400 --> 27:01.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What's all this about?

27:01.566 --> 27:04.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MATEA GOLD: So, we don't have a
lot of answers from the campaign
committee, which has declined

27:04.966 --> 27:07.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
to answer questions
about these payments.

27:07.166 --> 27:12.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But one thing we saw in the most
recent campaign finance filing
is that the legal fees paid

27:14.066 --> 27:17.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
