specifically was connected to

27:38.633 --> 27:40.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the Russian probe.

27:40.666 --> 27:44.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And there was also this
reimbursement to the
Trump corporation for
legal fees, which is

27:44.266 --> 27:49.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
the first time we have
seen Trump's own company
being reimbursed for
those kinds of service.

27:49.066 --> 27:52.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN YANG: What does the
Federal Election Commission
say about campaign funds being

27:52.933 --> 27:54.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
used for legal fees?

27:54.900 --> 27:58.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MATEA GOLD: The campaign
committees have a lot of leeway
to spend money on legal fees,

28:01.000 --> 28:04.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
