JUDY WOODRUFF: Right.

29:44.566 --> 29:48.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
AMY WALTER: When we
first started talking
about the president
after his inauguration,

29:48.166 --> 29:52.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
we said this is a president
