39:14.600 --> 39:19.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
AUBREY ADEN-BUIE: OSHA
investigated and called
that accident horrific
and preventable, and

39:20.466 --> 39:25.100 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
